Installed: Python, Node.js, Claude Code, vim, jq, git

Network Access:
  ✓ LLM APIs (Anthropic, OpenAI) - Available
  ✗ Internet - Restricted by default

To allow additional domains, run in a separate terminal:
  tsh beams allow --python-dev
  tsh beams allow --npm-dev
  tsh beams allow --github
  tsh beams allow --domain api.github.com

Quick start:
  claude --dangerously-skip-permissions

